Title: ðŸ”¥ [ANN] [PRE-ICO] INBET.IO First absolutely fair bookmaker (IBO)
Body: Since we are talking about competition, you, probably, would like to have a look at the bare facts and our dissimilarities from other betting services. Guaranteed payments by Ethereum smart contract. Transparency of transactions and payments. No account lockouts due to frequent wins. No account lockout due to arbitrage betting. No individually decreasing rates. Equal bet limits for each player. No rates of 1.0 or account freeze when withdrawing funds. Simplified registration and logging via MetaMask. No infrastructure risks associated with technical failures of equipment and interruptions in Internet connection. No risks of embezzlement. No Skype conferences, where you have to prove and beg the betting service to return your money. The highest rates in the market. No restrictions in access to invested money. Information security and confidentiality. Access from anywhere, at any time. The lowest margin in contrast with other betting services. InBet stability due to the entire Ethereum blockchain network; Safety of assets (accounts of players are placed on the smart contract account and are managed autonomously). You can keep constant control over your account and tokens, availability 24/7/365 from anywhere. You can use Windows, Mac, Linux or Android and iOS, as well as any browser. Blockchain and Ethereum smart contracts are a dynamically developing technology for investing, making deals on the Internet, and also for betting, and it would be a mistake to neglect all the advantages of this technology.
